              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI",
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The spectra of gamma rays were measured by",
                "a pair spectrometer that consisted of Ge(Li) detector",
                "63 cm3 in volume surrounded by a four-section ring",
                "NaI(Tl)detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Scandium films 1.2 and 1.7 micro-m thick obtained",
                "according to a procedure within which a thermal",
                "reduction of the scandium oxide Sc2O3 with thorium in",
                "a vacuum was followed by evaporation in a vacuum",
                "onto a tantalum substrate were used as targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STRUC",
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Radiative strength functions for E1",
                "transitions populating these states are determined. The",
                "resulting data are compared with predictions of various",
                "models."
              ]
            }
          ],
