          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The proton energy losses in a target were 40 to 80 keV",
                "in the energy range under study, and this in fact",
                "determined the widths of gamma lines in the spectra.",
                "For the degree of averaging to be adequate, the spectra",
                " of gamma rays measured at different proton energies",
                "were shifted in energy until the positions of gamma",
                "lines corresponding to primary gamma transitions became",
                "coincident, whereupon the spectra in question were",
                "summed. Primary transition intensities averaged over",
                "many compound nucleus resonances were determined via",
                "this summation of the spectra. Summation of six spectra",
                "led to the averaging interval deltaEp = 320 keV at Ep =",
                "2.63 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
